actions.message:
**How you gain XP**

**->** Be active in chat, you can only gain 15-25 xp once a minute. So spamming won't give you xp. If you spam tho, you'll get the SPAM role. With that role assigned, you will not longer be able to gain xp.

**How you see what rank/level you are**

**->** type !rank in #bot-spam to see your current XP-Status, level and rank.

**->** type !levels to see the Foxxi'sHouse Leaderboard

actions.fieldName: Do not brake these rules ;o Wumpus would have to hit you with the BAN-Hammer ;oo
actions.message:
1) Rules same as Twitch chat; no bigotry, racism, hate-speech, etc. 
2) Never sell out 
        -no linking any other streams
        -no "Woah, did you see that Blah Blah Blah is streaming?!?!"
3) Try not to rip eachother to shreds in comments
4) "Treat others the way that you want to be treated!" -Mom
5) Don't be a degenerate-meanieface-loser.
6) Don't post any NSFW content, or offensive images/memes here.
7) Any posts in the #general-english #pics-n-pets #art #fanarts  channels should either be LIT, funny, nice, awwwwww, or coolio
8) When in Voice Chat, please be courteous, and make it so we can't hear your open mouth breathing, keyboard smashing, or mouse clicking. 

NOTE: This is not a Discord Troubleshooting Server. If you are experiencing issues on Discord, please send in a support ticket here: https://dis.gd/contact

And if you're here to report a bad user, or someone breaking Discord's Terms of Service, please reach out to our Trust and Safety team here: https://dis.gd/request
